other_tests.findings: Prior to baricitinib treatment, monocytes from the patient displayed higher expression of all tested ISGs compared to healthy controls.
other_tests.changes_over_time: Expression of all five ISGs remarkably declined after initiation of baricitinib treatment.

other_tests.findings: T lymphocytes from the patient before and during treatment expressed higher levels of total STAT1 than that observed in healthy controls.
other_tests.changes_over_time: The enhanced pSTAT1 observed in patient T lymphocytes before baricitinib treatment was strongly reduced during treatment.
